[I] Open source groupware server for SOPE

[T] OpenGroupware.org is a set of applications for contact, appointment,
[T] project, and content management. It is comparable to Exchange and
[T] SharePoint portal servers. It is accessible using Web interfaces
[T] and various native clients, including Outlook. Its servers run on
[T] almost any GNU/Linux system, can synchronize with Palm PDAs, and
[T] are completely scriptable using XML-RPC.

[U] http://www.opengroupware.org/

